01:13:08,000 --> 01:13:11,000
We don't understand how life got started.

1174
01:13:11,000 --> 01:13:13,000
It did.

1175
01:13:13,000 --> 01:13:16,000
We don't understand how consciousness got started.

1176
01:13:16,000 --> 01:13:20,000
